---
title: Presto Chicken, Bacon and Mushroom Linguine with Tenderstem® and Cheese
description: Hey presto! This speedy Presto Chicken, Bacon and Mushroom Linguine is ready in under 25 minutes. Bacon acts as a cheat's pancetta here, tossed with chicken, mushrooms and fresh asparagus in a creamy sauce that's perfectly pleasing.
